Developer Terms of Use
des:
Ask someone for help. Ask someone to check a location in your home.
Find my phone. Arm or disarm your home security system by Alexa.
All of these services are free just by installing the free YouIPCams mobile app and create a free account.
Haicam Alexa app supports any ONVIF compatible cameras by YouIPCams mobile app.
Also, you can order Haicam end-to-end encryption security camera from Amazon or at https://haicam.tech/
